These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, martial-arts, satire
House: art-deco, modern, tower, cape-cod
1. the art-deco house is the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the tower house is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
4. the modern house is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
6. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
7. the modern house is on the far left or far right##3
8. the cape-cod house is between the person watching satire movies and the person who's hobby is hiking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | writing      | hiking | reading | skydiving |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | crime  | drama   | satire    |
| House     | art-deco     | tower    | cape-cod    | modern      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, singing, sudoku, video-games
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, alhambra, tiparillo, swisher
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
7. the chaman-smoker is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is singing##2
8. the swisher-smoker is between the alhambra-smoker and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | video-games | sudoku   | singing | dancing  |
| Cigar   | tiparillo     | chaman | swisher  | alhambra |
| Transport     | taxi        | jet-ski  | boat    | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
City: marseilles, paris, liverpool, hannover
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, canadian, german
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, snowmobile, train
1. the german is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person traveling to hannover##2
2. the argentine is the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is the person traveling to liverpool##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
5. the person traveling to hannover is in an odd position##4
6. the canadian is between the person traveling to paris and the american##2
7. the german is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| City          | marseilles | paris   | hannover     | liverpool     |
| Nationality   | argentine  | german | canadian   | american  |
| Transport     | train      | roller | snowmobile | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, horror, romance
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, brazilian, indian, french
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, rowing, tennis, water-polo
1. the french is in an even position##4
2. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the brazilian is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
5. the french is the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the person watching horror movies is the japanese##1
7. the indian is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | romance   | horror     | disaster |
| Nationality   | indian  | french      | japanese        | brazilian     |
| Sport         | tennis | badminton | water-polo | rowing   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, colombian, japanese
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, rugby, swimming, volleyball
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, fisherman, videographer, entrepreneur
1. the japanese is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the colombian is in an odd position##4
3. the lawyer is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the fisherman is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the lawyer is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
7. the canadian is on the far right##1
8. the colombian is on the left or right of the videographer##3
9. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | american   | japanese   | colombian | canadian |
| Sport         | rugby      | volleyball | golf      | swimming |
| Job     | fisherman | lawyer        | entrepreneur       | videographer  |

