.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, lemonade, tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, martial-arts, satire, time-travel
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, daisy, rose, tulip
1. the person who growsrose is the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person who growsdahlia##2
3. the person watching time-travel movies is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
7. the person watching comedy movies is the person drinking 7up##1
8. the person who growsrose is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | tea          | hot-chocolate | 7up        |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | martial-arts | time-travel   | comedy     |
| Flower           | dahlia | daisy         | tulip         | rose |

